=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
רבע / râba‛ / raw-bah'
=== Etymology ===

A primitive root (rather identical with {{HH|7250}} through the idea of sprawling at all fours (or possibly the reverse is the order of derivation); compare {{HH|702}}); 
=== Number ===
properly to be [[four]] (sided); used only as denominative of {{HH|7253}}; to be quadrate: - (four-) square (-d).